  <brief_title>Opioid Consumption After Knee Arthroscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Opioid Consumption After Knee Arthroscopy With and Without the Use of New Standardized Patient/Family Instructions for Postoperative Analgesic Use</official_title>
  <sponsors>
